代理揾鋪，夜晚就叫代理一起去翠園食飯，仲叫埋外賣，當然agent 埋單，之<span style=\"color: red;\">后</span>仲趁代理去厠所<span style=\"color: red;\">吾</span>為意，連筆都偷埋，跟著去埋松記磄水鋪叫野，加埋另叫外賣，之<span style=\"color: red;\">后</span>走時仲問代理有<span style=\"color: red;\">没</span>有$600，話明天會還，之后走了。再問落其他區同事先知，原來其他同行都見過呢個人。<br />\n<br />\n其實我做呢行都做好耐，但係佢真係呃人呃無破綻。去松記磄水鋪同個老闆吹水，講自己背景，又講識咩人咩人感，松記老闆又答得倒，等我信到十足。<br />\n仲要唔係我一個代理中招都算啦，係有幾個行家都中過招，好明顯呢個人，係熟手。<br />\n<br />\n地產代理唔易做，d 客睇完樓覺得唔<span style=\"color: red;\">岩</span>所以唔買，我完全理解，呢d野唔會迫都唔迫得。呢個人存心利用地產代理揾盤，之後 呃時間，呃錢，偷野，只過人真係太過份。<br />\n<br />\n呢個人渣真係好應該比其他街坊或代理知道有呢個人，以免受害。我自己係代理group己經po左呢條友出黎叫同事小心，都希望多d人知道呢一件事。<br />\n<br />\n行騙人電話<br />\nWi 鐘生 Vc 4room <br />\n+852 5170 6972<br />\n外區同事一樣中招<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6D2u2L5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6D2u2L5.jpg&h=9574e9c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2n081Gf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2n081Gf.jpg&h=46d55086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m4605d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm4605d0.png&h=0d22d65c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前睇樓D相，扮買家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1UDq9kK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1UDq9kK.jpg&h=452cfcf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/26YcnRB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F26YcnRB.jpg&h=284c0e34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Nm6o47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Nm6o47.jpg&h=ebda5e3f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d314d2665e9f997a0fb37c1ec92b9bda0c4c50f4","tid":180912,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:57:35.000Z","msg":"連個user名個字都錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 詐騙"},{"pid":"b9842dcffd544192e5170afbe0cbe03c872311c6","tid":180912,"uid":